### QueueForge API Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client or IntelliJ HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@workerId = worker-1
@queue = default

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health

### Prometheus Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/prometheus

### =========== JOBS ===========

### Submit a Job (log)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "queue": "default",
  "type": "example.log",
  "payload": { "msg": "hello" }
}

### Submit a Job (email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "queue": "default",
  "type": "example.email",
  "payload": { "to": "user@example.com", "subject": "Welcome" }
}

### Submit a Job (webhook)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "queue": "default",
  "type": "example.webhook",
  "payload": { "url": "https://example.com/hook", "method": "POST" }
}

### Submit a Job (report)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "queue": "default",
  "type": "example.report",
  "payload": { "reportName": "daily-summary", "format": "pdf" }
}

### Submit a Job (fail - for retry demo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "queue": "default",
  "type": "example.fail",
  "payload": { "message": "Simulated failure" },
  "maxAttempts": 2
}

### List Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobs?status=PENDING&size=5

### Get Job Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/jobs/{{jobId}}

### =========== WORKER ===========

### Get Worker Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workers/config

### Run Worker Once
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workers/{{workerId}}/run-once

### Manual Lease Single Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workers/{{workerId}}/lease?queue=default

### Recover Expired Leases
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/workers/recover-leases

### =========== ADMIN ===========

### Dashboard Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/dashboard/summary

### Queue Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/queues/stats

### Worker List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/workers

### Job Event Timeline
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/jobs/{{jobId}}/events

### Requeue Dead-Letter Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/jobs/{{jobId}}/requeue
Content-Type: application/json

{ "resetAttempts": true, "reason": "Manual retry" }

### Cancel Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/jobs/{{jobId}}/cancel

### Retry Job Now
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/jobs/{{jobId}}/retry-now
Content-Type: application/json

{ "resetAttempts": true }
